data.description: Discover your dream home in the heart of Coral Springs! This inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom townhouse is now available for sale in a highly desirable neighborhood known for its excellent schools and family-friendly neighborhood. It has spacious living areas filled with natural light. A large master suite with two additional bedrooms that are well-sized. You'll have easy access to parks, shopping, dining, and all that Coral Springs has to offer with convenient access to major highways, making it easy to reach nearby cities and attractions. "The Unit is Fresh Painted"
